class="meta-wrap clearfix"><div
class="author-meta u-h">
By <span
itemprop="author">Citylife</span> | Thu 12 Mar 2020<p
class="u-h" aria-hidden="true">
<time
itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2020-03-12T18:41:09+07:00>">
2020-03-12T18:41:09+07:00 </time>
<time
itemprop="dateModified" datetime="2020-04-25T19:41:32+07:00">
2020-04-25T19:41:32+07:00 </time></p></div></div><div
class="entry-content" itemprop="articleBody"><div
itemprop="summary"><p>Let us introduce you to the Chiang Mai locals.</p><p>Chiang Mai is a city bursting with talented, engaging, entrepreneurial and free-spirited people. We feature interviews and biographies of people from all walks of life. Some were born here others, from every corner of the world, chose to make Chiang Mai their home. Chiang Mai is truly a melting pot as you will discover as you browse these pages and meet some of our amazing Chiang Mai locals.</p></div><div
class="menu-page-articles"><div
